{"tid":663890,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"シャムキャッツ SIAMESE CATS LIVE IN HONG KONG","createTime":"2018-05-13T15:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T10:31:12.000Z","uid":79120,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f10c7c99c20647180451c04d10471ddfd7cb253f","tid":663890,"uid":79120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"シャムキャッツ SIAMESE CATS LIVE IN HONG KONG <br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n時間/Time : 20:00 <br />\n日期/Date: 21/6/2018<br />\n場地/Venue: MOM Live House <br />\nB39, 七海商業中心 113 - 121 英皇道, 北角<br />\n(炮台山 A 出口)<br />\nB39 , 7 Seas Shopping Centre,<br />\n113-121 King's Road, North Point <br />\n(Fortress Hill MTR Station Exit A) <br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n門票/ Ticket : $280 (預售adv.)/ $350(現場door)<br />\n預售票於以下店舖發售/ Ticketing Outlets:<br />\nWhite Noise Records <br />\n1/F, 720 Shanghai Street, Prince Edward, Kowloon, Hong Kong(Mongkok A2 EXIT)<br />\n<br />\nZoo Records <br />\nSHOP 325, 3/F PRESIDENT COMMERCIAL CENTRE, <br />\n608 NATHAN ROAD, MONGKOK, KOWLOON<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n-關於 シャムキャッツ SIAMESE CATS -<br />\n由主唱夏目知幸、吉他手菅原慎一、鼓手藤村頼正、貝斯手大塚智之4人共同組成的「 シャムキャッツ SIAMESE CATS 」 樸實中卻又帶著細膩的溫柔搖滾。<br />\n2009成立至今發行6張專輯，主唱夏目知幸軟綿的少年音，混搭著俏皮風與日常感，透過音樂捕捉了日常生活的小確幸與感動，在接踵而來的電吉他刷弦之中，彷彿陽光下的美好假期，很快就受到了注目。<br />\n<br />\n隨性的以「SIAMESE CATS（暹羅貓）」命名成軍，一路從下北澤「Daisy Bar」、東高圓寺「U.F.O.CLUB」，以及澀谷「TSUTAYA O-NEST」等Live House發跡。2016年創立了自主廠牌TETRA RECORDS，首次跨越國境，前往台北、韓國首爾演出。2017年發行最新專輯「Friends Again」，打出樂團新主軸&ldquo;plain（簡單／樸實）‧rock（搖滾）&rdquo;，可說是一張相當凸顯成員的個性的作品。 2017年他們也舉行了首次韓國、台灣、中國三地的亞洲巡迴，受到各地歌迷的熱烈支持，開始在亞洲嶄露頭角。<br />\n<br />\n(by BIG ROMANTIC RECORD)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2018358655148833/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2018358655148833%2F&d=p%2FQ8YAx%2B9tWhUHJpvOtT8y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4ff24a72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2018358655148833/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人去呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1852b3a545862dc38090a174350f0760969b99d5","tid":663890,"uid":79120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:38:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d00e61cd3f34a79e1b14b3fbc73e415db366b7","tid":663890,"uid":79120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"indie band無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dcd1bbd41c32718a7b67422733f82ea3bca4a8f","tid":663890,"uid":79120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T10:05:26.000Z","msg":"收工一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8572a87e3f8287648bd7692af54d41e9b9ecc34","tid":663890,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到post 開spotify望先知有聽過下佢地<br />\n未必去聽live但入黎推推"},{"pid":"89d08505e4dc1543c5b8c34afff8758fc3c3e08c","tid":663890,"uid":79120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8572a87e3f8287648bd7692af54d41e9b9ecc34","tid":663890,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到post 開spotify望先知有聽過下佢地<br />\n未必去聽live但入黎推推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於唔洗開post就10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6e3290984b60c2551b15c4ed459281b07c7a3e","tid":663890,"uid":89652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:09:51.000Z","msg":"拉埋朋友一齊去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好驚無人睇佢地"}